OOC: That's kinda funny. I can just see your face, "I'm a GUY!" Wow, 
that's good stuff. So very glad I joined the RPG now, you guys/girls 
seem like fun!

IC:

Vampirtron:

     He got off his rock and did a couple of flips, testing out the 
planets gravity. He wasn't able to jump as high as he had on his othe 
planet, but still high enough. He pulled out his two swords and swund 
them around, cutting into the trees as he did so. They worked well. 
He put them back and whipped out his claws. Nice and sharp claws.
     "I'm getting to like this place."
